
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-magma-snoop-12.txt'>
    <title>"Considerations for IGMP and MLD Snooping Switches", Morten Christensen, Karen Kimball, Frank Solensky</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-magma-snoop-12.txt</link>
    <description>This memo describes the recommendations for IGMP- and MLD-snooping switches. These are based on best current practices for IGMPv2, with further considerations for IGMPv3- and MLDv2-snooping. Additional areas of relevance, such as link layer topology changes and Ethernet-specific encapsulation issues, are also considered.</description>
    <dc:date>2005-02-24T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
